description.p:
One or more transmission formats may be defined for a UE. For example, a transmission format may be defined with the following:



    

1. A specific channelization code for the HS-PDSCH;

2. A specific modulation scheme (e.g., QPSK);

3. A specific transport block size;

4. HARQ-type information set to asynchronous IR, with pointer information to previous transmissions/retransmissions, two retransmissions and a predetermined sequence of redundancy versions; and

5. A UE-specific CRC.
